Databricks AWS Glue
Need to config the cluster-> go to Cluster->Spark->Config and add:
  spark.databricks.hive.metastore.glueCatalog.enabled true
Environment Variable 
   PYSPARK_PHTHON=/databricks/python3/bin/python3


